I know what Mr. Lu thinks.

76
00:04:02,890 --> 00:04:04,489
Will he stay if I confess

77
00:04:05,290 --> 00:04:06,489
my love to him?

78
00:04:08,049 --> 00:04:10,089
(Chun Menglong)
But he's meant to be a hero.

79
00:04:10,769 --> 00:04:11,890
How can I hold him back?

80
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:18,690
And I have so many house chores.

81
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:24,529
I shall stay with you
and mother forever.

82
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:45,920
She likes me.

83
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:48,576
She doesn't.

84
00:04:51,130 --> 00:04:52,289
She likes me.

85
00:04:58,570 --> 00:04:59,424
