- She likes...

86
00:05:01,370 --> 00:05:02,304
Peilan.

87
00:05:04,450 --> 00:05:06,130
Sorry, I lost my cool yesterday.

88
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:08,729
Mr. Lu, it was my fault.

89
00:05:09,769 --> 00:05:11,490
I should have said no to Mr. Li.

90
00:05:12,010 --> 00:05:13,890
But rest assured. I promise I'll return

91
00:05:14,130 --> 00:05:15,209
his shoes next time.

92
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:18,690
You're leaving soon.

93
00:05:19,250 --> 00:05:20,450
I hope you can

94
00:05:20,450 --> 00:05:22,490
stay cheerful and carefree.

95
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:25,984
Peilan.

96
00:05:26,969 --> 00:05:27,904
Peilan.

97
00:05:28,130 --> 00:05:29,440
Here you are, Peilan.

98
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,336
Mr. Li.

99
00:05:30,336 --> 00:05:31,264
Listen.

100
00:05:31,264 --> 00:05:32,409
Peilan.

101
00:05:32,409 --> 00:05:34,169
I picked the vegetables. Go and cook.

102
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:36,010
Mrs. Chun and my father will be hungry.

103
00:05:37,329 --> 00:05:38,272
No rush, Peilan.

104
00:05:38,529 --> 00:05:40,010
I'll talk to mother if she's mad.

105
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:41,810
Who's your "mother"?

106
00:05:42,849 --> 00:05:43,849
Why are you yelling?

107
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:45,440
What's wrong with you?

108
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:46,969
Peilan is your master.

109
00:05:46,969 --> 00:05:47,969
You're a servant.

110
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:50,649
How can a servant tell a master to cook?

111
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:52,089
Why do you care?

112
00:05:52,329 --> 00:05:53,450
It's a family affair.

113
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:55,769
Mind your words. Who's your "mother"?

114
00:05:56,289 --> 00:05:57,209
You won't shut up?

115
00:05:57,690 --> 00:05:59,610
"It's a family affair"?

116
00:05:59,769 --> 00:06:00,930
You're their family?

117
00:06:01,289 --> 00:06:02,769
Know your place.

118
00:06:02,890 --> 00:06:04,370
You're just their servant.

119
00:06:04,890 --> 00:06:05,856
What did you say?

120
00:06:05,856 --> 00:06:06,769
You're their servant.

121
00:06:06,769 --> 00:06:07,810
Let's go. One on one.

122
00:06:07,810 --> 00:06:08,672
Let's go.

123
00:06:08,672 --> 00:06:09,536
Wait.

124
00:06:11,849 --> 00:06:13,690
Mr. Li, since you're here,

125
00:06:14,089 --> 00:06:14,930
I'll bring your...

126
00:06:15,089 --> 00:06:15,936
Peilan.

127
00:06:17,209 --> 00:06:18,130
I got carried away.

128
00:06:18,649 --> 00:06:20,250
Actually, I came here

129
00:06:20,969 --> 00:06:22,969
to invite you to dinner.

130
00:06:23,810 --> 00:06:24,704
Dinner?

131
00:06:25,169 --> 00:06:26,209
Why?

132
00:06:26,209 --> 00:06:27,409
Because you gave me an egg.

133
00:06:28,529 --> 00:06:30,729
