at Spring River Restaurant at 18:00.

134
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,000
See you there.

135
00:06:33,409 --> 00:06:34,490
Mr. Li, I won't go.

136
00:06:35,370 --> 00:06:36,256
I just remembered.

137
00:06:36,649 --> 00:06:38,169
Young Lord is taking me to meet

138
00:06:38,169 --> 00:06:39,729
the new Assistant Minister of Justice.

139
00:06:40,089 --> 00:06:41,184
I have to go.

140
00:06:41,289 --> 00:06:42,450
I'll wait for you.

141
00:06:42,969 --> 00:06:44,529
Mr. Li, I won't go.

142
00:06:44,529 --> 00:06:45,690
Mr. Li, I won't go.

143
00:06:47,450 --> 00:06:49,890
Why doesn't he listen to me?

144
00:06:50,209 --> 00:06:51,072
An egg?

145
00:06:51,810 --> 00:06:53,250
What does he mean by "an egg"?

146
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:09,969
Master, your hand.

147
00:07:10,610 --> 00:07:11,450
Guo Zhensheng.

148
00:07:13,649 --> 00:07:14,769
What were you thinking?

149
00:07:14,769 --> 00:07:16,209
You almost cut your fingers!

150
00:07:16,409 --> 00:07:17,370
Why are you yelling?

151
00:07:17,370 --> 00:07:18,250
You scared me.

152
00:07:20,969 --> 00:07:22,050
I didn't sleep well.

153
00:07:23,648 --> 00:07:24,576
Banxia.

154
00:07:24,576 --> 00:07:26,592
Don't you think your mother is too kind

155
00:07:27,610 --> 00:07:28,512
to Master Lu?

156
00:07:28,610 --> 00:07:29,504
Isn't that normal?

157
00:07:31,130 --> 00:07:32,169
Normal?

158
00:07:35,130 --> 00:07:36,329
He's a guest.

159
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:38,656
Besides,

160
00:07:38,769 --> 00:07:40,930
Lu Buping has helped around a lot.

161
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:42,370
My mother may say mean things,

162
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:44,010
but she's grateful.

163
00:07:45,329 --> 00:07:47,130
Right, I just remembered.

164
00:07:48,130 --> 00:07:49,969
I heard that mother
asked you for ginseng

165
00:07:49,969 --> 00:07:51,810
to help Master Lu recover,
and you said no.

166
00:07:53,248 --> 00:07:54,176
Really?

167
00:07:56,370 --> 00:07:57,280
Master.

168
00:07:58,209 --> 00:08:00,370
Lu Buping has helped us
unload the herbs before.

169
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,112
You're too stingy.

170
00:08:02,729 --> 00:08:03,570
No.

171
00:08:03,570 --> 00:08:04,448
