172
00:08:04,849 --> 00:08:06,089
This is wrong.

173
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:07,392
Think about it.

174
00:08:08,409 --> 00:08:09,409
I'll get some herbs.

175
00:08:11,289 --> 00:08:12,192
Be careful.

176
00:08:13,810 --> 00:08:15,289
Even Banxia criticized me.

177
00:08:17,769 --> 00:08:19,409
Did I really do wrong?

178
00:08:20,769 --> 00:08:22,209
That's about it.

179
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:23,490
I don't know why Mr. Li

180
00:08:23,490 --> 00:08:25,169
cares so much about that egg.

181
00:08:25,169 --> 00:08:26,050
Of course, he cares.

182
00:08:26,570 --> 00:08:27,649
You helped him when he

183
00:08:27,649 --> 00:08:28,544
needed it the most.

184
00:08:29,570 --> 00:08:30,890
I know exactly how he feels.

185
00:08:31,450 --> 00:08:32,330
Mr. Lu,

186
00:08:32,569 --> 00:08:33,449
I swear it was just

187
00:08:33,449 --> 00:08:35,130
an innocent move.

188
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,096
- I was just...
- Peilan.

189
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:37,250
Come with us to Lu's Manor.

190
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,096
No.

191
00:08:40,289 --> 00:08:41,769
I know you'd be worried
about your family.

192
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:44,416
What if

193
00:08:44,809 --> 00:08:45,649
I tell my father?

194
00:08:47,169 --> 00:08:48,130
No.

195
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:49,289
He will call me a loser.

196
00:08:52,730 --> 00:08:53,664
Peilan,

197
00:08:53,809 --> 00:08:55,090
how can I just leave you?

198
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:56,768
Mr. Lu.

199
00:08:57,449 --> 00:08:58,336
Rest assured.

200
00:08:58,890 --> 00:09:01,090
I won't be in touch with him
after you leave.

201
00:09:01,610 --> 00:09:02,850
I worry the most about you.

202
00:09:03,409 --> 00:09:04,352
You're just saying that.

203
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:06,850
You can't reject people at all.

204
00:09:07,169 --> 00:09:08,569
You said you'd return his shoes.

205
00:09:08,689 --> 00:09:09,929
Now you have a dinner date.

206
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:11,689
I didn't agree to go.

207
00:09:11,689 --> 00:09:12,890
You heard me.

208
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:14,569
I did, but did he?

209
00:09:14,569 --> 00:09:16,569
How would I know if he did?

210
00:09:16,569 --> 00:09:18,409
Of course, he did

211
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:19,488
but ignored it.

212
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:36,169
Peilan, I'm sorry.

213
00:09:36,689 --> 00:09:38,210
I've been very irritable.

214
00:09:38,649 --> 00:09:39,730
I do want to create

215
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:41,850
some sweet memories before I leave.

216
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:44,090
B-But Li Tengyun keeps

217
00:09:44,449 --> 00:09:45,449
messing with us.

218
00:09:45,449 --> 00:09:48,010
Mr. Lu, can we stop talking about him?

219
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:49,890
He means nothing to us.

220
00:09:55,610 --> 00:09:58,010
Mr. Lu, don't be mad.

221
00:10:01,409 --> 00:10:02,529
Fine, I won't be.

222
00:10:07,730 --> 00:10:09,330
Your nose is bleeding.

223
00:10:14,890 --> 00:10:15,809
Mr. Lu.

224
00:10:16,370 --> 00:10:17,929
It's so easy to piss you off.

225
00:10:21,090 --> 00:10:22,090
Is he okay?

226
00:10:23,049 --> 00:10:23,970
Nothing serious.

227
00:10:24,689 --> 00:10:25,529
A rush of anxiety.

228
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,072
Mother scolded you again?

229
00:10:30,370 --> 00:10:31,569
I'll boil some medicine.

230
00:10:31,569 --> 00:10:33,049
Bring it to him later, Peilan.

231
00:10:33,649 --> 00:10:34,850
Rest well. Drink water.

232
00:10:35,449 --> 00:10:36,352
I'm leaving.

233
00:10:36,352 --> 00:10:37,248
Thank you, Banxia.

234
00:10:37,449 --> 00:10:38,336
No problem.

235
00:10:42,449 --> 00:10:43,970
Mr. Lu, take the day off.

236
00:10:45,049 --> 00:10:46,370
I'm fine. Let me help

237
00:10:46,730 --> 00:10:47,769
with all those chores.

238
00:10:48,449 --> 00:10:50,490
Banxia told you to rest and drink water.

239
00:10:51,610 --> 00:10:52,929
Just rest for a day.

240
00:10:53,370 --> 00:10:54,304
Where are you going?

241
00:10:55,449 --> 00:10:56,529
I'll make you something to eat.

242
00:10:57,569 --> 00:10:59,610
Rest assured.
I won't go anywhere tonight.

243
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:17,730
What's wrong? Are you sick?

244
00:11:21,610 --> 00:11:22,528
Are you sick?

245
00:11:23,049 --> 00:11:23,936
No.

246
00:11:24,569 --> 00:11:27,169
The shopkeeper
of the rouge store is busy.

247
00:11:27,169 --> 00:11:28,250
I'm bringing her the medicine.

248
00:11:38,090 --> 00:11:39,529
Do I look sick?

249
00:11:48,769 --> 00:11:49,632
Peilan.

250
00:11:50,330 --> 00:11:51,200
Peilan.

251
00:11:51,649 --> 00:11:52,576
Peilan.

252
00:11:53,529 --> 00:11:55,330
Peilan, I waited for four hours.

253
00:11:55,330 --> 00:11:56,210
Where were you?

254
00:11:56,449 --> 00:11:57,449
I was worried that

255
00:11:57,449 --> 00:11:58,769
something went wrong.

256
00:11:58,769 --> 00:12:00,169
So I rushed here.

257
00:12:00,169 --> 00:12:01,024
- I just...
- Mr. Li.

258
00:12:01,809 --> 00:12:03,169
I told you I wouldn't go.

259
00:12:03,529 --> 00:12:05,250
And Mr. Lu is sick.
I'm taking care of him.

260
00:12:06,169 --> 00:12:07,072
Lu Buping?

261
00:12:07,649 --> 00:12:08,809
Is he pulling a trick?

262
00:12:09,210 --> 00:12:10,144
Of course not.

263
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:12,224
Fine.

264
00:12:13,529 --> 00:12:15,809
It's late. Thankfully, you're fine.

265
00:12:15,809 --> 00:12:17,090
Maybe tomorrow...

266
00:12:18,449 --> 00:12:19,360
Mr. Li.

267
00:12:19,610 --> 00:12:21,210
Please don't come to me again.

268
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:23,929
And wait here.

269
00:12:24,449 --> 00:12:25,344
Peilan.

270
00:12:28,169 --> 00:12:30,250
Mr. Li, you'd better refund your shoes.

271
00:12:30,449 --> 00:12:31,296
Go home.

272
00:12:31,569 --> 00:12:32,480
Peilan.

273
00:12:32,569 --> 00:12:34,210
B-But worn items are not refundable.

274
00:12:34,610 --> 00:12:35,488
Peilan.

275
00:12:36,289 --> 00:12:37,152
Peilan.

276
00:12:37,689 --> 00:12:38,689
What happened, Peilan?

277
00:12:39,370 --> 00:12:40,288
Peilan.

278
00:12:48,890 --> 00:12:49,792
Mr. Lu.

279
00:12:50,289 --> 00:12:51,850
I made some soothing herbal tea.

280
00:12:53,130 --> 00:12:54,048
Thank you.

281
00:12:54,850 --> 00:12:55,769
Are you better?

282
00:12:57,250 --> 00:12:59,409
I'm fine. It's just some nosebleed.

