00:13:01,370 --> 00:13:02,970
I'll cut some wood today.

284
00:13:03,809 --> 00:13:05,929
You're leaving. So stop working.

285
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:07,104
It's okay.

286
00:13:07,210 --> 00:13:08,370
You'll do all the work

287
00:13:08,610 --> 00:13:09,730
once I'm gone.

288
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,490
I might as well do more now.

289
00:13:12,610 --> 00:13:15,610
It's fine.
I'll do those little by little...

290
00:13:21,250 --> 00:13:22,569
Li Tengyun, it's you again?

291
00:13:23,130 --> 00:13:24,610
Peilan, I'm cutting wood for you.

292
00:13:25,689 --> 00:13:26,610
Mr. Li.

293
00:13:28,049 --> 00:13:28,960
Morning, Jinrong.

294
00:13:32,370 --> 00:13:33,248
Go ahead.

295
00:13:33,649 --> 00:13:34,769
What did the Young Lord say?

296
00:13:35,809 --> 00:13:37,210
Nothing for now.

297
00:13:40,610 --> 00:13:42,049
So why are you here?

298
00:13:42,370 --> 00:13:43,689
I'm helping Peilan.

299
00:13:47,250 --> 00:13:48,130
Mr. Li.

300
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:50,130
You've been lurking around Peilan

301
00:13:50,449 --> 00:13:51,529
these days.

302
00:13:52,049 --> 00:13:52,928
Right?

303
00:13:53,610 --> 00:13:54,528
Not exactly.

304
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,210
I just hate to see

305
00:13:56,210 --> 00:13:58,610
Peilan doing so many chores.

306
00:13:59,010 --> 00:14:01,850
And your only servant is a weakling

307
00:14:02,049 --> 00:14:02,970
who just fell sick.

308
00:14:04,010 --> 00:14:05,169
Li Tengyun, make it clear.

309
00:14:05,289 --> 00:14:06,370
Who's a weakling?

310
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:10,049
Peilan works hard.
I'm taking care of her.

311
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:11,569
Stop sweet-talking her.

312
00:14:11,970 --> 00:14:13,490
It's none of your business.

313
00:14:14,809 --> 00:14:15,712
Lu Buping.

314
00:14:15,890 --> 00:14:17,409
You're so ungrateful.

315
00:14:18,049 --> 00:14:20,490
Peilan told me
that you were sick last night.

316
00:14:20,490 --> 00:14:22,409
That's why I'm here to help around.

317
00:14:22,809 --> 00:14:23,744
Seriously.

318
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:24,896
Last night?

319
00:14:26,090 --> 00:14:27,130
So you met last night?

320
00:14:27,890 --> 00:14:28,769
You said you wouldn't go.

321
00:14:28,769 --> 00:14:30,929
No, he came here to see me.

322
00:14:32,169 --> 00:14:33,088
He came here?

323
00:14:34,449 --> 00:14:35,330
You...

324
00:14:35,330 --> 00:14:36,192
You...

325
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,730
What else are you hiding from me?

326
00:14:38,730 --> 00:14:39,712
Nothing.

327
00:14:40,224 --> 00:14:41,120
Lu Buping.

328
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,176
Don't touch me.

329
00:14:42,176 --> 00:14:43,040
Come on.

330
00:14:43,169 --> 00:14:45,610
Does Peilan have to
report everything to you?

331
00:14:46,049 --> 00:14:47,130
Who do you think you are?

332
00:14:48,210 --> 00:14:49,056
Peilan.

333
00:14:49,569 --> 00:14:51,289
Should I get the dry clothes?

334
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:53,649
Mr. Li, please go home.

335
00:14:54,130 --> 00:14:55,449
I can handle these chores.

336
00:14:56,449 --> 00:14:57,890
Okay, I'll go on with the wood.

337
00:15:00,250 --> 00:15:01,090
Drop the axe now.

338
00:15:02,090 --> 00:15:02,970
Mr. Lu, calm down.

339
00:15:02,970 --> 00:15:04,130
- Your nose will bleed.
- Give me.

340
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:04,970
- Go away.
- Mr. Lu.

341
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:06,976
Mr. Lu.

342
00:15:07,330 --> 00:15:08,449
- Take it easy.
- Li Tengyun.

343
00:15:08,769 --> 00:15:09,664
You...

344
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:12,330
Mr. Lu, your...

345
00:15:12,330 --> 00:15:14,010
your nose is bleeding again.

346
00:15:15,850 --> 00:15:17,970
You can take care of Peilan like that?

347
00:15:18,169 --> 00:15:19,529
I bet Peilan is taking care of you.

348
00:15:19,689 --> 00:15:21,010
Should I help her with that?

349
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:23,490
Y-You've crossed the line.

350
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:26,368
Are you ready?

351
00:15:26,368 --> 00:15:27,232
Yeah.

352
00:15:31,689 --> 00:15:32,608
Master Lu.

353
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:33,809
Great stamina.

354
00:15:33,809 --> 00:15:35,330
You play better than my master.

355
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:39,744
Good shot.

356
00:15:39,744 --> 00:15:40,689
Master Lu.

357
00:15:41,649 --> 00:15:42,569
Mrs. Chun.

358
00:15:42,569 --> 00:15:43,850
Come for water

359
00:15:43,850 --> 00:15:45,250
if you're tired.

360
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:46,144
All right, Mrs. Chun.

361
00:15:46,370 --> 00:15:47,210
I'm not tired, Mother.

362
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:49,792
Come and join us.

363
00:15:49,970 --> 00:15:51,890
No way, I'm too old for this.

364
00:15:51,890 --> 00:15:53,809
Mrs. Chun, exercise is good for health.

365
00:15:56,569 --> 00:15:57,490
One more.

366
00:16:03,010 --> 00:16:04,569
Nice move.

367
00:16:04,569 --> 00:16:05,649
Keling, take it.

368
00:16:05,649 --> 00:16:07,569
Guo Zhensheng.

369
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:13,090
Perhaps

370
00:16:16,890 --> 00:16:19,169
it's time to give up.

371
00:16:31,569 --> 00:16:32,480
Peilan.

372
00:16:33,504 --> 00:16:34,409
Peilan.

373
00:16:34,409 --> 00:16:35,296
Mr. Lu.

374
00:16:35,649 --> 00:16:36,576
Mr. Lu.

375
00:16:37,610 --> 00:16:38,464
You woke up.

376
00:16:38,689 --> 00:16:39,569
Are you better?

377
00:16:42,449 --> 00:16:43,392
Peilan.

378
00:16:44,090 --> 00:16:45,169
I lost a lot of blood.

379
00:16:46,409 --> 00:16:47,689
Don't tell my father.

380
00:16:48,610 --> 00:16:50,529
I didn't want to worry him
so I didn't tell him.

381
00:16:51,850 --> 00:16:52,704
That's good.

382
00:16:56,010 --> 00:16:56,850
Is Li Tengyun gone?

383
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:00,064
Yeah.

384
00:17:03,169 --> 00:17:04,064
Help me up.

385
00:17:05,249 --> 00:17:06,969
Mr. Lu, stay down.

386
00:17:07,290 --> 00:17:08,449
Rest a bit longer.

387
00:17:09,449 --> 00:17:11,009
Sorry, it's all my fault.

388
00:17:12,009 --> 00:17:13,130
How is it your fault?

389
00:17:13,890 --> 00:17:15,610
He's too shameless.

390
00:17:16,330 --> 00:17:18,770
I've never seen such a shameless person.

391
00:17:22,610 --> 00:17:23,520
He's awake?

392
00:17:24,370 --> 00:17:25,409
Peilan, feed him.

393
00:17:25,610 --> 00:17:26,528
Okay.

394
00:17:26,784 --> 00:17:27,712
Mr. Lu, have the medicine.

395
00:17:27,712 --> 00:17:28,576
I can do it myself.

396
00:17:31,890 --> 00:17:32,736
Slowly.

397
00:17:33,689 --> 00:17:35,810
Oh right, Li Tengyun brought the herbs.

398
00:17:35,810 --> 00:17:37,090
Thank him once you recover.

399
00:17:37,489 --> 00:17:38,336
Okay.

400
00:17:40,370 --> 00:17:41,729
Mr. Lu, what are you doing?

401
00:17:43,050 --> 00:17:44,890
When is he going to stop?

402
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:47,249
Mr. Lu, come on.

403
00:17:47,449 --> 00:17:49,409
Don't be mad. You already drank some.

404
00:17:49,729 --> 00:17:51,009
That rascal is pestering you.

405
00:17:52,130 --> 00:17:53,850
Mr. Lu, rest assured.

406
00:17:53,850 --> 00:17:55,449
How can I rest assured?

407
00:17:55,449 --> 00:17:56,969
I have to leave but I just can't.

408
00:18:00,770 --> 00:18:01,850
There's only one solution.

409
00:18:03,330 --> 00:18:04,256
What is it?

410
00:18:06,489 --> 00:18:07,424
Come with me.

411
00:18:08,610 --> 00:18:10,330
Mr. Lu, I'm not going to Lu's Manor.

412
00:18:10,330 --> 00:18:11,570
We're not going there.

413
00:18:12,009 --> 00:18:12,928
We're going to Dali.

414
00:18:12,928 --> 00:18:13,824
Didn't I say I'd

415
00:18:13,824 --> 00:18:14,784
take you there?

416
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:16,810
I'm serious.

417
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:18,688
I say we should

418
00:18:19,610 --> 00:18:20,544
leave tonight.

419
00:18:20,890 --> 00:18:21,810
Just the two of us.

420
00:18:21,810 --> 00:18:23,169
Nobody will ever bother us.

421
00:18:23,449 --> 00:18:24,530
Your father is still here.

422
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:25,890
I'll leave him a letter.

423
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:29,169
I believe he's going to understand.

424
00:18:31,409 --> 00:18:32,649
But I...

425
00:18:33,969 --> 00:18:34,848
Peilan.

426
00:18:35,570 --> 00:18:37,050
I know you care about your family.

427
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:39,008
Be brave for me

428
00:18:39,330 --> 00:18:40,370
just once, please.

429
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:42,370
Abandon everything.

430
00:18:42,649 --> 00:18:43,770
Let's find our happiness.

431
00:18:44,050 --> 00:18:45,489
As long as we're happy,

432
00:18:45,649 --> 00:18:46,649
your mother and my father

433
00:18:47,169 --> 00:18:48,649
will be happy for us.

434
00:18:48,850 --> 00:18:49,696
Really.

435
00:19:18,810 --> 00:19:19,744
Ruyu.

436
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:25,536
I'm leaving.

437
00:19:29,169 --> 00:19:30,249
I wish you happiness.

438
00:19:38,090 --> 00:19:39,008
What are you doing?

439
00:19:40,610 --> 00:19:41,568
Just passing by.

440
00:19:41,689 --> 00:19:43,290
I stewed the chicken soup the whole day.

441
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:44,192
Let's go have some.

442
00:19:45,169 --> 00:19:46,112
You

443
00:19:46,770 --> 00:19:48,449
asked me for ginseng

444
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:51,130
to make chicken soup for me?

445
00:19:51,449 --> 00:19:52,352
No.

446
00:19:53,009 --> 00:19:53,929
It's for everyone.

447
00:19:56,249 --> 00:19:57,120
By the way.

448
00:19:57,290 --> 00:19:58,729
Tidy up Keling's room later.

449
00:19:58,729 --> 00:19:59,729
She will sleep there.

450
00:20:00,810 --> 00:20:01,728
Where is Lu Jiang?

451
00:20:02,370 --> 00:20:03,328
He's gone.

452
00:20:03,969 --> 00:20:04,890
Where is Lu Buping?

453
00:20:04,890 --> 00:20:05,770
Also gone.

454
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:07,489
That's why you'll tidy up the room.

455
00:20:08,249 --> 00:20:09,152
Have some soup first.

456
00:20:11,570 --> 00:20:12,544
Where are you going?

457
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:13,929
You told me to

458
00:20:14,409 --> 00:20:15,330
tidy up the room.

459
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:16,810
It's more urgent than the soup.

460
00:20:29,890 --> 00:20:31,169
What's taking her so long?

461
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,640
(To My Father Lu Jiang)

462
00:20:47,249 --> 00:20:48,224
Father.

463
00:20:48,729 --> 00:20:49,664
I'm sorry.

464
00:20:51,249 --> 00:20:53,530
Peilan and I are going to
pursue our happiness.

465
00:20:55,689 --> 00:20:56,608
Peilan.

466
00:20:58,009 --> 00:20:59,449
F-Father.

467
00:20:59,449 --> 00:21:00,649
W-What are you doing here?

468
00:21:01,090 --> 00:21:02,009
Am I still your father?

469
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:04,032
What...

470
00:21:14,530 --> 00:21:16,929
Mr. Lu.

471
00:21:21,409 --> 00:21:22,969
Help, someone robbed my purse.

472
00:21:23,050 --> 00:21:23,969
Don't worry, Miss.

473
00:21:24,449 --> 00:21:27,290
I came down the mountain
to do people justice.

474
00:21:29,090 --> 00:21:30,449
I brought you another quilt.

475
00:21:30,610 --> 00:21:32,249
So you won't
fight over it in your sleep.

476
00:21:32,969 --> 00:21:33,824
Thank you.

477
00:21:35,360 --> 00:21:35,969
Hot?

478
00:21:35,969 --> 00:21:36,570
Are you okay?

479
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:37,249
I'm fine.

480
00:21:39,449 --> 00:21:40,352
Are you okay?

481
00:21:42,409 --> 00:21:43,850
Why are you so careless, Lu Buping?

482
00:21:46,249 --> 00:21:47,168
Open it.

483
00:21:53,330 --> 00:21:54,810
Look, shooting stars.

484
00:22:07,610 --> 00:22:08,544
Uncle Lu,

485
00:22:08,850 --> 00:22:09,890
I'm so sorry that

486
00:22:10,689 --> 00:22:12,850
I agreed to go to Dali with him
behind your back.

487
00:22:13,890 --> 00:22:15,810
It's because he was in so much pain.

488
00:22:16,969 --> 00:22:17,810
He will wait for me

489
00:22:18,090 --> 00:22:19,449
at the city gate
from 7:00 PM to 9:00 PM.

490
00:22:20,370 --> 00:22:21,248
Take him away.

491
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:26,169
A short-lived pain
is better than a lasting agony.

492
00:22:26,570 --> 00:22:28,130
Mr. Lu may feel hurt but he will

493
00:22:28,130 --> 00:22:29,009
forget me soon.

494
00:22:35,209 --> 00:22:36,209
You're a good girl.

495
00:22:37,890 --> 00:22:39,090
I didn't expect you to be

496
00:22:40,449 --> 00:22:41,449
so considerate of him.

497
00:22:42,969 --> 00:22:44,169
Thank you for that.

498
00:22:47,209 --> 00:22:48,064
Uncle Lu,

499
00:22:50,050 --> 00:22:51,810
this is the sword tassel I made for him.

500
00:22:52,649 --> 00:22:53,689
Please bring it to him.

501
00:22:55,330 --> 00:22:56,224
(I'm sure he'll)

502
00:22:57,009 --> 00:22:58,929
(become a well-respected hero.)

503
00:23:05,209 --> 00:23:06,090
Look at you.

504
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,320
You're a grown man.

505
00:23:08,649 --> 00:23:09,890
But Peilan is much more mature.

506
00:23:10,169 --> 00:23:11,249
You wanted to run off with her?

507
00:23:12,489 --> 00:23:13,344
What will happen

508
00:23:14,209 --> 00:23:15,530
to Peilan and her family?

509
00:23:17,449 --> 00:23:19,290
You think running off solves everything?

510
00:23:20,729 --> 00:23:21,729
You're not being brave.

511
00:23:22,530 --> 00:23:23,456
You're escaping.

512
00:23:24,409 --> 00:23:25,312
But, Father,

513
00:23:26,969 --> 00:23:28,449
I don't want to go back.

514
00:23:29,050 --> 00:23:30,090
I like Peilan.

515
00:23:31,249 --> 00:23:32,770
I like my life here.

516
00:23:33,330 --> 00:23:34,330
Just answer me.

517
00:23:35,969 --> 00:23:36,969
Are you coming back with me?

518
00:23:40,969 --> 00:23:41,850
No.

519
00:23:41,850 --> 00:23:42,816
Are you?

520
00:23:43,810 --> 00:23:44,672
No.

521
00:23:50,050 --> 00:23:51,449
Good boy.

522
00:23:57,130 --> 00:23:58,048
You've grown up.

523
00:23:58,729 --> 00:23:59,680
If a man

524
00:24:00,610 --> 00:24:02,290
can't protect his love,

525
00:24:03,449 --> 00:24:04,770
then he's no hero even if

526
00:24:05,850 --> 00:24:07,009
he masters martial arts.

527
00:24:20,209 --> 00:24:21,130
If you agree to

528
00:24:22,290 --> 00:24:23,689
go home with me,

529
00:24:25,050 --> 00:24:26,449
you truly let Peilan down.

530
00:24:31,290 --> 00:24:33,570
I've been an upright man my whole life.

531
00:24:34,449 --> 00:24:36,050
I've never done anything I regret

532
00:24:37,249 --> 00:24:38,249
except that I haven't

533
00:24:42,890 --> 00:24:44,050
kept your mother company.

534
00:24:52,370 --> 00:24:53,216
I'm leaving.

535
00:24:56,090 --> 00:24:56,992
Father.

536
00:24:58,890 --> 00:24:59,776
Remember.

537
00:25:00,130 --> 00:25:01,409
Keep training.

538
00:25:01,969 --> 00:25:02,880
Got it, Father.

539
00:25:12,890 --> 00:25:14,969
Father, that boat is sailing to Dali.

540
00:25:18,689 --> 00:25:20,689
A romantic trip is exactly what I want.

541
00:25:54,409 --> 00:25:55,610
Greetings, Grandmother.

542
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:01,824
Mind your steps.

543
00:26:07,009 --> 00:26:07,904
Sit down.

544
00:26:16,330 --> 00:26:17,209
What were you thinking?

545
00:26:18,370 --> 00:26:19,264
Nothing.

546
00:26:20,409 --> 00:26:21,330
It's getting chilly.

547
00:26:21,810 --> 00:26:23,290
You should rest in your room.

548
00:26:24,489 --> 00:26:25,449
The Imperial Physicians

549
00:26:25,449 --> 00:26:27,090
said that Her Majesty
has almost recovered

550
00:26:27,530 --> 00:26:28,689
and should walk more.

551
00:26:32,689 --> 00:26:33,632
Oh, right.

552
00:26:33,729 --> 00:26:36,050
You mentioned crepe cake last time.

553
00:26:36,330 --> 00:26:38,489
I sent someone to get me some.

554
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:40,370
The folk foods

555
00:26:40,969 --> 00:26:42,770
may not have the best ingredients,

556
00:26:42,770 --> 00:26:44,969
but they do taste quite exotic.

557
00:26:46,209 --> 00:26:47,050
It's really good.

558
00:26:57,890 --> 00:26:59,169
What delicious food

559
00:26:59,249 --> 00:27:00,610
did you buy for our boss?

560
00:27:02,209 --> 00:27:03,249
Your favorite crepe cake.

561
00:27:04,850 --> 00:27:06,409
Boss, you're really prescient.

562
00:27:08,090 --> 00:27:09,024
Your Highness.

563
00:27:11,009 --> 00:27:11,936
Your Highness.

564
00:27:15,689 --> 00:27:17,449
Are you bothered by something?

565
00:27:19,370 --> 00:27:20,288
Grandmother,

566
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:22,090
I'd like to go out again.

567
00:27:23,249 --> 00:27:24,160
Your Highness.

568
00:27:24,409 --> 00:27:27,009
You're just back and have barely
kept Her Majesty company.

569
00:27:27,449 --> 00:27:28,330
You're leaving again?

570
00:27:31,449 --> 00:27:32,416
There is someone

